Test case #:  Content Assist on NLclass methods

Steps to recreate problem:
1.create a C++/Managed Make C++ Project
2.import TestData/CA
3.uncomment the line:
    // n->
4.place the cursor after the "->" and press [ALT + /](I've already changed the 
hot key from [CTRL + SPACE] to [ALT + /]

Error: it doesn't popup a dialog

Expected Result: popup a dialog with code assist


