2.import TestData/CA
3.uncomment the line:
    // int i = fun
4.place the cursor after the "fun" and press [ALT + /](I've already changed the 
hot key from [CTRL + SPACE] to [ALT + /]

Error: it doesn't popup a dialog(After I press [ALT + /], it will change the 
       word from "fun" to "funNLfunction2". And I press [ALT + /] again, it 
       will change the word "funNLfunction2" to "funNLfunction1", then
       "funNLfunction1" to "funxon2", "funxon2" to "function1", "function1" 
       to "fun" repeatly.)

